      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 63 },
      "id": 61,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Health Check Runbook\n\n| Metric | Good | Warning | Action |\n|--------|------|---------|--------|\n| **Task Running Ratio** | ≥ 0.95 | < 0.95 | Check connector logs, restart if needed |\n| **Queue Utilization** | < 70% | 70-90% | Monitor for back-pressure, may need tuning |\n| **CPU Usage** | < 70% | > 80% | Scale Connect workers or reduce load |\n| **Heap Utilization** | < 80% | > 85% | Increase heap size or investigate memory leak |\n| **Producer Error Rate** | 0 | > 0 | Check broker connectivity, topic permissions |\n| **Lag (ms behind source)** | < 5000 | > 30000 | Check Oracle performance, connector config |\n\n**Common Issues:**\n- Task FAILED: Check logs for errors, verify Oracle connectivity and XStream setup\n- High queue utilization: Kafka write slowness, increase `max.queue.size` or tune producer\n- Zero throughput: Verify Oracle capture is running, check table.include.list patterns\n- High lag: Oracle under load, increase connector tasks or optimize queries"
      },
      "title": "Health Check & Troubleshooting",
      "type": "text"
